snippet: North Carolina State pestered No. 2 Notre Dame defensively, fought to a draw on the boards and never let the Fighting Irish get their high-scoring offense rolling in transition....
lead_paragraph: North Carolina State pestered No. 2 Notre Dame defensively, fought to a draw on the boards and never let the Fighting Irish get their high-scoring offense rolling in transition.

headline.main: NC State Women Hold On to Upset No. 2 Notre Dame 70-62
